metadata.description:
“Yaki Onigiri（Grilled Rice Ball）" is a traditional Japanese food that has existed since BC.
Now, the “Yaki Onigiri” has been transformed and is attracting attention as "Yaki Onigiri with Wings(Rice cracker).
This project is to gather friends to spread this new Japanese food, a fusion of tradition and innovation, worldwide.
Funds raised will be used to expand the business around the world.
NFT holders will receive a new limited edition NFT when they eat a grilled onigiri at the store (scheduled to begin at the Tokyo (Iriya) main store after September 2022). We can also develop the business as a new business partner.
metadata.name: YAKI ONIGIRI TOWN #1
